race.comment: BRONZE (7) wasn't far away at the finish when 5th and beaten only 2.5 lengths (26.11) at this track. Should bounce back. HANDSOME RATIO (3) was quickly out of the boxes with a slick early sectional clocking 19.36 with a 2.25 lengths win at Healesville over 350m. Ran the fastest time on the program in his latest win. Makes plenty of appeal if runs up to latest. BUSH LASS (1) carved over from wide out and boxed on strongly to finish 1.75 lengths away in second (25.54) behind Pete's Entity at Warrnambool. Was a winner at her only start from this draw. Expecting another good run. BINDY BLAZER (8) is in the mix after placing at a big quote last time out.
